reviewText: This is one of the classic city girls series. I like it. At least it's not one of those really slow motion too many girls in a scene movies. This is at least worth a rent if you find a video rental store. Don't bother viewing this if you are a hardcore porn viewer or a fast pace type softcore lover.
honestly, and truly, you can get much better stuff off the nets, or even off of cable.  your money would be better spent somewhere else!
